				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/09/11/16991-tarifs-energetiques-appauvrissons-le-peuple-mais-progressivement?replytocom=88130#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-88130", "88130", "respond", "16991")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
		</article>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
